sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Cliente/Aplicación
    participant MainProxy as ConsultaPlanesCredito.proxy
    participant RutaRegional as consultaRutaRegional_db
    participant NIProxy as ConsultaPlanesCreditoNI.proxy
    participant ConvertPais as convertirCodigoPais
    participant NIDatabase as MasterData/conDatosPlanes_db
    participant NIOracle as Oracle Database NI
    participant MapeoErrores as MapeoErrores.proxy
    participant ErrorHandler as Manejador de Errores

    Note over Client, ErrorHandler: Flujo Nicaragua (NI01) - ConsultaPlanesCredito

    Client->>MainProxy: SOAP Request
    Note right of Client: Header: SourceBank=NI01<br/>Body: ACCOUNT_NUMBER, ORG

    MainProxy->>MainProxy: Validar Esquema XML
    Note right of MainProxy: Validar campos obligatorios<br/>ACCOUNT_NUMBER no vacío

    alt Validación Fallida
        MainProxy->>ErrorHandler: Error de Validación
        ErrorHandler->>MainProxy: Respuesta de Error
        MainProxy->>Client: SOAP Fault
    end

    MainProxy->>RutaRegional: Consultar Ruta Regional
    Note right of RutaRegional: ServiceId: FICBCO0321<br/>Region: NI01<br/>Version: V2

    RutaRegional->>RutaRegional: Consultar BD Regional
    
    alt Región No Válida
        RutaRegional->>MainProxy: PV_CODIGO_ERROR != SUCCESS
        MainProxy->>MapeoErrores: Mapear Error Regional
        MapeoErrores->>MainProxy: Error Mapeado
        MainProxy->>Client: Response con Error
    end

    RutaRegional->>MainProxy: PV_UBICACION=ConsultaPlanesCreditoNI
    Note left of RutaRegional: PV_CODIGO_ERROR=SUCCESS<br/>PV_UBICACION=Middleware/v2/ProxyServices/ConsultaPlanesCreditoNI

    MainProxy->>MainProxy: Enrutamiento Dinámico
    Note right of MainProxy: Router Dinámico:<br/>service=ConsultaPlanesCreditoNI

    MainProxy->>NIProxy: Invocar Proxy NI
    Note right of NIProxy: Transport: LOCAL<br/>SOAP Selector: SOAP action<br/>(DIFERENTE a GT/HN)

    NIProxy->>ConvertPais: Convertir Código País
    Note right of ConvertPais: Conversión: NI01 → NIC<br/>Sentido: OSB-ISO3<br/>fn:string() explícito

    ConvertPais->>NIProxy: Código País Convertido
    Note left of ConvertPais: Resultado: NIC

    NIProxy->>NIProxy: Transformar Request (XQuery)
    Note right of NIProxy: conDatosPlanesIn.xq<br/>Mapear ACCOUNT_NUMBER → PV_CUENTA<br/>Mapear ORG → PV_ORG<br/>Mapear NIC → PV_CODIGO_PAIS

    NIProxy->>NIProxy: Validar Request DB
    Note right of NIProxy: Validar esquema XSD<br/>MasterData/conDatosPlanes/xsd/conDatosPlanes_sp<br/>Namespace: con4:InputParameters

    NIProxy->>NIDatabase: Invocar Stored Procedure
    Note right of NIDatabase: Connection: eis/DB/ConnectionTarjetas<br/>SP: OSB.dbo.OSBConDatoPlanes<br/>(ÚNICO con SchemaName=OSB)

    NIDatabase->>NIOracle: CALL OSB.dbo.OSBConDatoPlanes(PV_CUENTA, PV_ORG, PV_CODIGO_PAIS)
    
    alt Error en Base de Datos
        NIOracle->>NIDatabase: CodigoError != -1
        NIDatabase->>NIProxy: Response con Error
        NIProxy->>NIProxy: Construir Error Response
        Note right of NIProxy: successIndicator: ERROR<br/>messages: validationMessage
        NIProxy->>MainProxy: Response con Error
        MainProxy->>MapeoErrores: Mapear Error
        MapeoErrores->>MainProxy: Error Mapeado
        MainProxy->>Client: Response con Error
    end

    NIOracle->>NIDatabase: ResultSet con Planes
    Note left of NIOracle: CodigoError: -1<br/>MensajeError: vacío<br/>RowSet con datos:<br/>- org, cuenta, numseq<br/>- logo, numplan, total_due<br/>- tipo_plan, int_rate<br/>- int_rat1_base, balanceactual<br/>- fecplan, acrd_int<br/>- mora_acrd_int, d2ps_mora_int_per_diem

    NIDatabase->>NIProxy: Response Exitoso

    NIProxy->>NIProxy: Validar Response DB
    Note right of NIProxy: Verificar errorCode != '-1'<br/>Si error: validationMessage = MensajeError<br/>Si éxito: validationMessage = ''

    NIProxy->>NIProxy: Transformar Response (XQuery)
    Note right of NIProxy: consultaPlanesCreditoOut.xq<br/>Mapear campos de BD a response:<br/>- org → ORG<br/>- cuenta → ACCOUNT<br/>- numseq → SEQ_NUMBER<br/>- logo → LOGO<br/>- numplan → PLAN_NUMBER<br/>- total_due → PAY_MINIMUM<br/>- tipo_plan → TYPE_PLAN<br/>- int_rate → INT_RATE<br/>- int_rat1_base → INT_RATE_BASE<br/>- balanceactual → CURRENT_BALANCE<br/>- fecplan → DATE_PLAN (yyyyMMdd)<br/>- acrd_int → ACRD_INT<br/>- mora_acrd_int → DELAYS_ACRD_INT<br/>- d2ps_mora_int_per_diem → ACCUMULATED_DELAYS_INT

    NIProxy->>NIProxy: Construir Header de Respuesta
    Note right of NIProxy: Si validationMessage vacío:<br/>successIndicator: Success<br/>Si error:<br/>successIndicator: ERROR<br/>messages: validationMessage

    NIProxy->>MainProxy: SOAP Response
    Note left of NIProxy: Header: successIndicator=Success<br/>Body: CREDIT_PLANS con array de CREDIT_PLAN<br/>Variable: $RSPconDatosPlanes (minúscula)

    MainProxy->>MainProxy: Validar Response Final
    Note right of MainProxy: Verificar successIndicator != SUCCESS

    alt Response con Error
        MainProxy->>MapeoErrores: Mapear Error Final
        Note right of MapeoErrores: CODIGO_ERROR: successIndicator<br/>MENSAJE_ERROR: FICBCO0321$#$messages
        MapeoErrores->>MainProxy: Error Homologado
        MainProxy->>MainProxy: Actualizar Header Response
    end

    MainProxy->>Client: SOAP Response Final
    Note left of Client: Header: successIndicator, messages<br/>Body: Planes de crédito estructurados<br/>con información completa por plan

    Note over Client, ErrorHandler: Transformaciones Clave NI01:
    Note over Client, ErrorHandler: 1. Código País: NI01 → NIC (OSB-ISO3)
    Note over Client, ErrorHandler: 2. Fecha: DateTime → yyyyMMdd
    Note over Client, ErrorHandler: 3. Validación: errorCode != '-1' = éxito
    Note over Client, ErrorHandler: 4. Conexión BD: eis/DB/ConnectionTarjetas
    Note over Client, ErrorHandler: 5. SP: OSB.dbo.OSBConDatoPlanes (CON SchemaName=OSB)
    Note over Client, ErrorHandler: 6. Transport: LOCAL (sin HTTP endpoint)
    Note over Client, ErrorHandler: 7. SOAP Selector: SOAP action (no body)
    Note over Client, ErrorHandler: 8. Error Handling: successIndicator=ERROR estándar
    Note over Client, ErrorHandler: 9. Variable Response: $RSPconDatosPlanes (minúscula)
    Note over Client, ErrorHandler: 10. Namespace: con4:InputParameters en validación
    Note over Client, ErrorHandler: 11. Conversión País: fn:string() explícito